    "id": "f_csv_bea1fa792a",
    "slug": "caste-is-a-delicate-issue-it-s-ubiquitous-and-we-are-full-of-it-we-should-sta",
    "texto": "Caste is a delicate issue. It's ubiquitous, and we are full of it. We should start to change things from individual level. But when you go to people and deny caste, they may not react favourably. I think if a decisive percentage of people, especially elites, start marrying out of their caste, we may see a casteless India in a generation's time.",
